" Ignore errornous input in Mac OS X
imap <D-space> <Nop>

" <Ctrl-Space> invokes <C-X><C-O> (omni-completion)
inoremap <C-Space> <C-x><C-o>
inoremap <C-@> <C-x><C-o>

" window navigation
noremap <C-h> <C-w>h
noremap <C-j> <C-w>j
